quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  16,30,WE KILE LILLEDHINE ETTEKAW MADHA ‘ENZELE REBBUKUM KALU HAJRÆN LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA HESENETUN WE LEDARUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN WE LENI’ME DARUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,31,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU LEHUM FIHA MA JESHA’UNE KEDHALIKE JEXHZI ELLAHUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,32,EL-LEDHINE TETEWEFFAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU TEJJIBINE JEKULUNE SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUMU EDHULUL-XHENNETE BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,33,HEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA ‘EN TE’TIJEHUMUL-MELA’IKETU ‘EW JE’TIJE ‘EMRU RABBIKE KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE MA DHELEMEHUMU ELLAHU WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  16,34,FE’ESABEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA ‘AMILU WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  16,35,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA ‘ABEDNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN NEHNU WE LA ‘ABA’UUNA WE LA HERREMNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FEHEL ‘ALA ER-RUSULI ‘ILLAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,36,WE LEKAD BE’ATHNA FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULÆN ‘ENI EU’BUDU ELLAHE WE EXHTENIBUT-TAGUTE FEMINHUM MEN HEDALLAHU WE MINHUM MEN HEKKAT ‘ALEJHI ED-DELALETU FESIRU FIL-’ERDI FANDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  16,37,‘IN TEHRIS ‘ALA HUDAHUM FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDI MEN JUDILLU WE MA LEHUM MIN NASIRINE
  16,38,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LA JEB’ATHU ELLAHU MEN JEMUTU BELA WA’DÆN ‘ALEJHI HEKKÆN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,39,LIJUBEJJINE LEHUMUL-LEDHI JEHTELIFUNE FIHI WE LIJA’LEMEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEHUM KANU KADHIBINE
  16,40,‘INNEMA KAWLUNA LISHEJ’IN ‘IDHA ‘EREDNAHU ‘EN NEKULE LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  16,41,WEL-LEDHINE HAXHERU FI ELLAHI MIN BA’DI MA DHULIMU LENUBEWWI’ENNEHUM FI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE LE’EXHRUL-’AHIRETI ‘EKBERU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  16,42,EL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  16,43,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM FAS’ELU ‘EHLE EDH-DHIKRI ‘IN KUNTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,44,BIL-BEJJINATI WE EZ-ZUBURI WE ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE EDH-DHIKRE LITUBEJJINE LILNNASI MA NUZZILE ‘ILEJHIM WE LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,45,‘EFE’EMINEL-LEDHINE MEKERU ES-SEJJI’ATI ‘EN JEHSIFEL-LAHU BIHIMUL-’ERDE ‘EW JE’TIJEHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  16,46,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM FI TEKALLUBIHIM FEMA HUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  16,47,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM ‘ALA TEHAWWUFIN FE’INNE REBBEKUM LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  16,48,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ILA MA HALEKAL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN JETEFEJJE’U DHILALUHU ‘ANIL-JEMINI WE ESH-SHEMA’ILI SUXHXHEDÆN LILLAHI WE HUM DAHIRUNE
  16,49,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI MIN DABBETIN WEL-MELA’IKETU WE HUM LA JESTEKBIRUNE
  16,50,JEHAFUNE REBBEHUM MIN FEWKIHIM WE JEF’ALUNE MA JU’UMERUNE